    "body" : "<p>To answer your question very directly, look at Map.Entry.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/Map.Entry.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Map.Entry</a></p>\n\n<p>also this may be useful</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://littletutorials.com/2008/03/06/static-nested-interfaces/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Static Nested Inerfaces blog Entry</a></p>\n"
