    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you will change class Foo into interface Foo the \"public\" keyword in the above example will be also redundant as well because </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>interface defined inside another interface will <strong>implicitly public\n  static.</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n"
  }, {
